import React from 'react' import './Card.css' import axios from '../axios/axios' import { useEffect,useState } from 'react' function Card() { const [Damimg, setDamimg] = useState('') const [Dam,setDam]=useState("") useEffect(() => { axios.get('/images').then((response)=>{ console.log(response.data.damImage) setDamimg(response.data.damImage) axios.get('/dam-details').then((res)=>{ console.log(res.data) setDam(res.data) }) }) }, []) return ( <>
Dam name
{Dam.damName}
Project id
{Dam.projectId}
Inspection Start Date
{Dam.inspectionStartDate}
Inspection end Date
{Dam.inspectionEndDate}
River
{Dam.river}
Location of dam
{Dam.location}
) } export default Card
